      • shouldForceReturnIDLE

        public boolean shouldForceReturnIDLE()
        If the method returns false at the end of the IDLE animation the pet won't be forced to it's original position
        Returns:
        True if at the end of the IDLE animation the pet is forced back to it's original location. False if at the end of the IDLE animation the pet is not forced back to it's original location
